Here is a example of readme.xml file :
<?xml version="1.0"?>
<readme>
  <document>
    <title>Sample</title>
    <file>sample.ps</file>
    <type>public</type>
    <author>First Author</author>
    <author>Second Author</author>
    <date>16 January 2002</date>
    <language>English</language>
    <summary>A little sample</summary>
    <part>Introduction</part>
    <part>Index</part>
    <comment>	
      <author_name>Julien LEMOINE</author_name>
      <content>This is a comment</content>
    </comment>
    <comment>	
      <author_name>Julien LEMOINE</author_name>
      <content>Second comment</content>
    </comment>
  </document>
</readme>

here is a example of command :
  orgadoc -r -p /var/www/docs -w -e /tmp
